page.title: 20Acknowledgements
page.content: This report was produced by the following primary schools during the summer term of 1985 and is a small sample of written work produced.We would like to thank all who contributed and to the communities who offered much of the information. As all the written material was edited we are not acknowledging any individual. {High Lane}surveyed by: Brookside Primary and Doodfield Primary. {Hazel Grove}surveyed by: Norbury C of E Primary,Norbury Hall Junior and Torkington Primary. {Poynton}surveyed by Poynton Vernon Junior School.
